docs {
  # Increment Counter
  Atomically increments a Redis counter by 1.
  
  **Route:** `POST /api/counter/increment/:key`
  
  Replace `:key` with the counter name.
  
  Returns the new counter value after increment.
  Creates counter if it doesn't exist (starts at 1).
}
